	<h1 class="title">看过那么多段子了，为什么还要看段子手的书？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-14 13:25:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9575/medium/9575.jpg?1436675644" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


